data.description: This is a quality home nestled in on Willow Pond Frontage!  It does not get much better than this to own a lovely one level 3 bed, 2 bath home with an open floor plan in such a peaceful setting! A property like this does not come around often! The home has been well cared for and not enough can be said about the outdoor living! Enjoy the summer living with the built in swimming pool or hanging out around the pond.  Winters could be just as enjoyed with the Avalon wood stove. The property is gated with a fenced yard and pasture, and do not forget the charming seasonal creek. The home and property are truly a must that should be DEFINETLY added to your check out list!!!!!
